members.name: U_USING_FALLBACK_WARNING
members.comment: < A resource bundle lookup returned a fallback result (not an error)

members.name: U_USING_DEFAULT_WARNING
members.comment: < A resource bundle lookup returned a result from the root locale (not an error)

members.name: U_SAFECLONE_ALLOCATED_WARNING
members.comment: < A SafeClone operation required allocating memory (informational only)

members.name: U_STATE_OLD_WARNING
members.comment: < ICU has to use compatibility layer to construct the service. Expect performance/memory usage degradation. Consider upgrading

members.name: U_STRING_NOT_TERMINATED_WARNING
members.comment: < An output string could not be NUL-terminated because output length==destCapacity.

members.name: U_SORT_KEY_TOO_SHORT_WARNING
members.comment: < Number of levels requested in getBound is higher than the number of levels in the sort key

members.name: U_AMBIGUOUS_ALIAS_WARNING
members.comment: < This converter alias can go to different converter implementations

members.name: U_DIFFERENT_UCA_VERSION
members.comment: < ucol_open encountered a mismatch between UCA version and collator image version, so the collator was constructed from rules. No impact to further function

members.name: U_PLUGIN_CHANGED_LEVEL_WARNING
members.comment: < A plugin caused a level change. May not be an error, but later plugins may not load.

members.name: U_MISSING_RESOURCE_ERROR
members.comment: < The requested resource cannot be found

members.name: U_INVALID_FORMAT_ERROR
members.comment: < Data format is not what is expected

members.name: U_FILE_ACCESS_ERROR
members.comment: < The requested file cannot be found

members.name: U_INTERNAL_PROGRAM_ERROR
members.comment: < Indicates a bug in the library code

members.name: U_MESSAGE_PARSE_ERROR
members.comment: < Unable to parse a message (message format)

members.name: U_INDEX_OUTOFBOUNDS_ERROR
members.comment: < Trying to access the index that is out of bounds

members.name: U_INVALID_CHAR_FOUND
members.comment: < Character conversion: Unmappable input sequence. In other APIs: Invalid character.

members.name: U_ILLEGAL_CHAR_FOUND
members.comment: < Character conversion: Illegal input sequence/combination of input units.

members.name: U_INVALID_TABLE_FORMAT
members.comment: < Conversion table file found, but corrupted

members.name: U_BUFFER_OVERFLOW_ERROR
members.comment: < A result would not fit in the supplied buffer

members.name: U_UNSUPPORTED_ERROR
members.comment: < Requested operation not supported in current context

members.name: U_RESOURCE_TYPE_MISMATCH
members.comment: < an operation is requested over a resource that does not support it

members.name: U_NO_SPACE_AVAILABLE
members.comment: < No space available for in-buffer expansion for Arabic shaping

members.name: U_CE_NOT_FOUND_ERROR
members.comment: < Currently used only while setting variable top, but can be used generally

members.name: U_PRIMARY_TOO_LONG_ERROR
members.comment: < User tried to set variable top to a primary that is longer than two bytes

members.name: U_STATE_TOO_OLD_ERROR
members.comment: < ICU cannot construct a service from this state, as it is no longer supported

members.name: U_TOO_MANY_ALIASES_ERROR
members.comment:
< There are too many aliases in the path to the requested resource.
											 It is very possible that a circular alias definition has occurred

members.name: U_ENUM_OUT_OF_SYNC_ERROR
members.comment: < UEnumeration out of sync with underlying collection

members.name: U_INVARIANT_CONVERSION_ERROR
members.comment: < Unable to convert a UChar* string to char* with the invariant converter.

members.name: U_INVALID_STATE_ERROR
members.comment: < Requested operation can not be completed with ICU in its current state

members.name: U_COLLATOR_VERSION_MISMATCH
members.comment: < Collator version is not compatible with the base version

members.name: U_USELESS_COLLATOR_ERROR
members.comment: < Collator is options only and no base is specified

members.name: U_NO_WRITE_PERMISSION
members.comment: < Attempt to modify read-only or constant data.

members.name: U_MALFORMED_RULE
members.comment: < Elements of a rule are misplaced

members.name: U_MALFORMED_UNICODE_ESCAPE
members.comment: < A Unicode escape pattern is invalid

members.name: U_MISPLACED_ANCHOR_START
members.comment: < A start anchor appears at an illegal position

members.name: U_MISPLACED_CURSOR_OFFSET
members.comment: < A cursor offset occurs at an illegal position

members.name: U_MISPLACED_QUANTIFIER
members.comment: < A quantifier appears after a segment close delimiter

members.name: U_UNDEFINED_SEGMENT_REFERENCE
members.comment: < A segment reference does not correspond to a defined segment

members.name: U_UNDEFINED_VARIABLE
members.comment: < A variable reference does not correspond to a defined variable

members.name: U_UNQUOTED_SPECIAL
members.comment: < A special character was not quoted or escaped

members.name: U_UNTERMINATED_QUOTE
members.comment: < A closing single quote is missing

members.name: U_RULE_MASK_ERROR
members.comment: < A rule is hidden by an earlier more general rule

members.name: U_MISPLACED_COMPOUND_FILTER
members.comment: < A compound filter is in an invalid location

members.name: U_INVALID_RBT_SYNTAX
members.comment: < A "::id" rule was passed to the RuleBasedTransliterator parser

members.name: U_VARIABLE_RANGE_EXHAUSTED
members.comment: < Too many stand-ins generated for the given variable range

members.name: U_VARIABLE_RANGE_OVERLAP
members.comment: < The variable range overlaps characters used in rules

members.name: U_ILLEGAL_CHARACTER
members.comment: < A special character is outside its allowed context
